BepInEx.Priconne
================

An independent BepInEx 6 (IL2CPP) mod loader build for Princess Connect! Re:Dive.
This product is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1 (see LICENSE).

It is a fork / re-assembly of the open BepInEx lineage. The following upstream projects
are incorporated or referenced; their licenses and attribution are preserved:

- BepInEx (https://github.com/BepInEx/BepInEx) — LGPL-2.1. The core loader framework
  (preloader, chainloader, Unity IL2CPP runtime, UnityDoorstop integration).
- Il2CppInterop (https://github.com/BepInEx/Il2CppInterop) — the IL2CPP <-> managed interop
  runtime (class injection, signature scanning, Cpp2IL-generated assemblies). The shipped
  build includes the FindSignatureInModule scan-safety fix contributed upstream.
- c01ns/Il2CppDumper (https://github.com/c01ns/Il2CppDumper) — the metadata-version 39 parser
  (Perfare/Il2CppDumper lineage) used for offline interop generation.
- krulci (https://github.com/krulci) — the open Priconne BepInEx / PrincessDumper lineage this
  build descends from and re-wires onto current tooling.

